dc.title: NASA Langley Media and Public Outreach Offices
dc.description: This is a NASA Langley Research Center (LaRC) Office of External Affairs (OEA) homepage. OEA is made up of Langley's media and public outreach offices. Currently, this link will take you to the News section of the LaRC home page -- http://www.nasa.gov/centers/langley/news/
